All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Application
The entry point of the entire application.
BinaryExpression
Represents a binary expression in a formula or computation.
BooleanValue
A final class representing a boolean value in an expression.
CellReference
A record representing a cell reference in a spreadsheet, which includes the row, column, and a string identifier.
CellReference.WithText
A record representing a cell reference with associated text content.
CellReferenceException
Exception thrown when there is an issue with cell references, such as invalid coordinates or identifiers.
CellReferenceExpression
Represents an expression that refers to a specific cell in a spreadsheet or table.
CellReferenceJsonDeserializer
A custom JSON deserializer for CellReference objects, extending JsonDeserializer.
CellReferenceJsonSerializer
A custom JSON serializer for CellReference objects, extending JsonSerializer.
Configuration
A record that encapsulates all the configuration settings for an application.
Constants
A utility class that holds constant values used throughout the application.
ContainerBasedDataAccessor
A simple implementation of the DataAccessor interface that acts as a wrapper around a DataContainer.
CustomCellEditor
A custom cell editor for editing Data objects in a JTable representing a spreadsheet.
CustomCellReferenceModule
A custom Jackson module for handling the serialization and deserialization of CellReference objects.
CustomCellRenderer
A custom cell renderer for the cells of a JTable that represents a spreadsheet.
Data
Represents the data associated with a cell in a table-like structure, including the cell's text, its evaluated value, and an optional expression tree for cells containing formulas.
DataAccessException
Custom exception to handle data access related errors.
DataAccessor
Interface for accessing Data by a CellReference.
DataContainer
The DataContainer class manages a table-like structure for storing and retrieving data associated with specific CellReference instances.
DataDependencyException
Exception thrown when there is a problem with data dependencies.
DataFactory
Interface for creating Data instances based on a given cell text.
DataManager
Interface for managing data within a table-like structure.
DataSelfReferenceException
Exception thrown when a data item references itself, which is not allowed.
DataWatcher
Interface for monitoring and responding to changes in data within a table or similar structure.
DebugPanel
A panel that displays debugging information about the currently selected cell in the spreadsheet.
DependencyGraph
Interface for managing dependencies between CellReference instances in a data graph.
DoubleValue
A final class representing a double value in an expression.
Expression
Abstract base class for all expression types within the expression parsing and evaluation framework.
ExpressionEvaluationException
Exception thrown when there is an error in evaluating an expression.
ExpressionEvaluator
An interface for evaluating expressions.
ExpressionParser
An interface for parsing expressions into Expression objects.
ExpressionParsingException
Exception thrown when an error occurs while parsing an expression.
ExtensionBasedFileManager
An implementation of the FileManager interface that determines the appropriate file adapter based on the file extension.
FileAdapter
Interface defining methods for saving and loading data to and from files.
FileException
Base class for exceptions related to file operations.
FileManager
Interface for managing file operations related to data persistence.
FileMenu
A custom file menu for the spreadsheet application, extending JMenu.
FileReadException
Exception thrown when there is an error reading data from a file.
FileType
Enum representing different file types used in the application.
FileWriteException
Exception thrown when there is an error writing data to a file.
Function
An enum representing various built-in functions that can be evaluated in expressions.
FunctionArgumentException
Exception thrown when a function receives an incorrect number of arguments.
FunctionExpression
Represents an expression that involves a function and its arguments.
FunctionOperator
Represents a function operator used in expressions, encapsulating a Function.
FunctionUtils
Utility class that provides logic for evaluating common functions, such as sum, count, and average, on a range of numeric values.
IntegerValue
A final class representing an integer value in an expression.
IterableValue
A final class representing a value that holds a collection of Value instances.
JacksonSerializationFileAdapter
Implementation of FileAdapter for handling file operations using Jackson serialization.
JsonConfig
A utility class for configuring and providing an ObjectMapper instance for JSON processing.
KeyBindingsConfigurator
A utility class for configuring key bindings for a SpreadsheetTable.
MainFrame
The main window for the spreadsheet application, extending JFrame.
MenuBar
A custom menu bar for the spreadsheet application, extending JMenuBar.
NonFunctionOperator
Represents a non-function operator used in expressions, such as arithmetic or comparison operators.
NonFunctionOperator.Associativity
Enum representing the associativity of an operator.
NonFunctionOperator.Type
Enum representing the different types of non-function operators.
Operator
An abstract class representing a general operator used in expressions.
RangeExpression
Represents a range of cells in a spreadsheet, defined by a start and end CellReference.
RangeParsingException
Exception thrown when an error occurs while parsing a range expression.
RowHeaderRenderer
A custom cell renderer for the row headers of a JTable.
ShuntingYardParser
An implementation of the ExpressionParser interface that uses the Shunting Yard algorithm to parse mathematical expressions into an Expression object.
SimpleDataFactory
A simple implementation of the DataFactory interface that creates Data instances based on the provided cell text.
SimpleDataManager
A simple implementation of the DataManager interface that manages data in a table-like structure.
SimpleDataWatcher
A simple implementation of the DataWatcher interface that monitors and manages dependencies between cells in a table-like structure.
SimpleExpressionEvaluator
A simple implementation of the ExpressionEvaluator interface.
SimpleTokenizer
A simple implementation of the Tokenizer interface, responsible for breaking down an input string into a list of Token objects.
SpreadsheetFileChooser
A custom file chooser for the spreadsheet application, extending JFileChooser.
SpreadsheetTable
A custom table component for displaying and interacting with a spreadsheet.
SpreadsheetTableModel
A table model for the spreadsheet application, extending AbstractTableModel.
StringValue
A final class representing a string value in an expression.
Token
Represents a token used in parsing expressions.
Token.Type
Enum representing the different types of tokens that can be encountered in an expression.
Tokenizer
An interface for tokenizing strings into a list of Token objects.
TopologicallySortedDependencyGraph
Implementation of the DependencyGraph interface that manages dependencies between CellReference instances using a topological sorting approach.
Value
An abstract sealed class representing a value that can be used in expressions and evaluated.
ValueCastException
Exception thrown when an invalid type cast operation is attempted on Value objects.
ValueExpression
Represents an expression that holds a constant Value.
